title: Big Sean Slapped By Man At Autograph Signing In Queens
text:
Home > Music > Big Sean Slapped By Man At Autograph Signing In Queens Big Sean Slapped By Man At Autograph Signing In Queens 0 0 Posted by Danny Schwartz , Feb 18, 2017 at 09:58am "What did the five fingers say to the face?" 
A Big Sean meet-and-greet autograph signing at F.Y.E. in Ridgewood, Queens was cut short Friday evening after a man apparently slapped Sean the face. 
Video footage shows a man being held down by multiple police officers. The cameraman explains why: he had just slapped Big Sean. 
As the man is placed in cuffs, he yells "You pussy, nigga!" and shouts out Birdman . The incident effectively cancelled the remainder on the event. As police escorted the man out of the building, he told Sean to "tell Jay Z wassup." dude smacked big sean then said tell jay-z I said what's up pic.twitter.com/2Fd9qRD8iM
